post_text:
Congratulations to the EHS Science Olympiad squad for their accomplishments at the Pembroke Hill Science Olympiad Meet. As a team, they placed 8th out of 26 schools!

EHS Science Olympiad students placing in the top 10 at the Pembroke Hill Science Olympiad meet were:

Astronomy-KJ/Kira, 10th; Boomilever-Kaden/ Ryleigh, 8th;

Chemistry Lab-KJ/Natalie, 9th;

Disease Detectives-KJ/Natalie, 8th;

Dynamic Planet-Steven, 10th

We are very #EudoraProud of you!

